76561197991341199,Recommended,290300,18668875,"Posted: 24 October, 2015",all,SimpliG,"Tl/dr: It is a really fun and nice game from some Indie developers, and while there are some bugs and exploit possibilites in the game, the devs throw patchs from day to day, so in a short time I'm sure they will be all gone. It is definetly worth its price, for 20 bucks you get 20+ hours of fun, far better than a cinema!------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------The gameplay is simple, but if you got the vibe of it, it's hard to stop playing. It's not a space-sim, but a more arcade-ish game with a very strong atmosphere. catchy soundtrack (which you can extend/replace with your own music from your hard drive if it's not your style), Beatiful skyboxes, plenty and mesmerizing explosions, laser projectiels and engine trails.The combat is really fun, you have to position well so you can fire with your main weapons on the side of the ship. It might be a bit challenging first but as soon as you learn the tricks and how to sail in the blins spot of the other ships, it becomes much easier, but stays as fun as in the begining. there is no better feeling when you destroy a ship 3-4 times bigger than yours on your own.The controls are made for controlers mainly, and many people say that keyboard+mouse is bad, but personally i had no problem with it, only when you aim with the turrets, the camera can stick to strange places, but it doesn't matter as they will be on auto fire 80% of the time, while you ahndle the broadside guns.The story mission is a bit short and simple, and sadly many characters get only a little screen time. But the dialoges are really well written. Overall if you rush the game it can be finished pretty quickly(possible evein in 5-10 hours, but if you fiddle around it can last up to 25-30 hours! it took me around 20 hours to finish the main story [while i did plenty of sandbox stuff] and other 3 hours to get tthe best stuff in the game.), but even if you get the best weapons and defensises on your favorit ship, the combat is still fun and you can spend a hour easily to blast some poor souls into the space."
