,Not Recommended,290300,28300677,"Posted: 10 December, 2016",all,Graymaven,"To be honest, I was really rooting for this game. I'm a space junkie, if it's set in the stars I am SO there. I was hoping this would be something I would love but... no.The game looks very pretty, the ships are unique enough in design and the environments are great.The game is a 2.5D tabletop space game, you are a capital ship that moves in 2D with the rest fo the capital ships while smaller fighters and bombers move in 3D.  In theory this is meant to reflect your weight/lack of maneuverability as a capital ship and streamline combat/movement.  In practice, it makes combat with other capital ships boring and combat with smaller fighters frustrating. The story is threadbare at best, consisting of a string of fetch quests narrated by badly acted npcs.Don't waste your money here."
